com.jivesoftware.selenium.pagefactory.framework.browser.web

Class RemoteBrowser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jivesoftware.selenium.pagefactory.framework.browser.Browser<org.openqa.selenium.WebDriver>
      • com.jivesoftware.selenium.pagefactory.framework.browser.web.WebBrowser
        • com.jivesoftware.selenium.pagefactory.framework.browser.web.RemoteBrowser

  • public class RemoteBrowser
extends WebBrowser

    Represents a RemoteBrowser, i.e. running a Browser on a Selenium Node controlled by a Selenium Hub. To create an instance, pass in the "delegate" browser and the URL to the Selenium Hub. Example Selenium Hub URL: http://hub.my.company.com:4444/wd/hub

    See http://code.google.com/p/selenium/wiki/Grid2
